<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p><a title="Companies > Com2uS [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/com2us">Com2uS</a> has <a href="https://arank-party-ridatsu-official.com/information/%e3%82%b2%e3%83%bc%e3%83%a0%e5%8c%96%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a%ef%bc%81%ef%bc%81/" target="_blank">announced</a> a game based on the isekai light novel and anime <em><a title="Games > I Left My A-Rank Party to Help My Former Students Reach the Dungeon Depths!" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/i-left-my-a-rank-party-to-help-my-former-students-reach-the-dungeon-depths">I Left My A-Rank Party to Help My Former Students Reach the Dungeon Depths!</a></em> The official title, genre, and supported platforms were not announced. Com2uS traditionally makes iOS and Android games, but <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/12/gachiakuta-the-game-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-and-pc" target="_blank">recently announced</a> <em><a title="Games > GACHIAKUTA: The Game [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gachiakuta-the-game">GACHIAKUTA: The Game</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>. <span id="more-1037200"></span></p><p>Watch the announcement trailer below. Follow the game on Twitter <a href="https://twitter.com/Aparidagame" target="_blank">here</a>.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="TVアニメ「Aランクパーティを離脱した俺は、元教え子たちと迷宮深部を目指す。」ゲーム化決定PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LWqgOr6pV04?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
